le is a flowering herb belonging to the daisy family. In traditional Ayurvedic practices, milk thistle can be used for problems related to the liver, owing to an active ingredient called Silymarin, which is an essential antioxidant that may have protective effects on the liver. neuherbs Milk Thistle capsules contain 800 mg of Silymarin and can help maintain liver health, reduce body inflammation, and improve overall health naturally.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (60 Capsules)","offer_id":40975847620778,"sku":"NMT60","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"2 Months Pack - (120 Capsules)=Recommended","offer_id":44266746740906,"sku":"NMT60P2","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/bestmilkthistlesupplement.jpg?v=1713168571"},{"product_id":"ashwagandha-1000-plus-tablets-stress-relief","title":"Ashwagandha 1000 Plus Tablets – Daily Lifestyle Support","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eneuherbs Ashwagandha 1000 Plus is made with natural ashwagandha root extract, Vitamin E, and B-complex (B6, B9, B12), along with piperine. This blend is designed to \u003cstrong data-start=\"1412\" data-end=\"1497\"\u003ehelp maintain balance, support an active lifestyle, and promote everyday wellness\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":40975944614058,"sku":"NA1000P60","price":319.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"2 Months Pack - (120 Tablets)=Recommended","offer_id":41395707478186,"sku":"NA1000P60P2-1","price":598.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/ashwagandha_tablets_1000_plus_1.jpg?v=1754394534"},{"product_id":"glucosamine-plus-tablets","title":"Neuherbs Glucosamine Plus Tablets","description":"\u003cp\u003eneuherbs 6-in-1 Glucosamine Formula combines 1500 mg Glucosamine with 1000 mg MSM, Chondroitin, and added collagen-supporting nutrients to Repair, Rebuild, Lubricate \u003cbr\u003eRegenerate, Cushion, Protect joints and to deliver highly effective joint nourishment. This \u003cbr\u003eadvanced glucosamine blend is designed for better absorption and targeted support, \u003cbr\u003ehelping protect cartilage while assisting in the repair of joint tissues and the rebuilding of \u003cbr\u003ecollagen fibers. Enhanced with Vitamin C and Hyaluronic Acid, the glucosamine tablet \u003cbr\u003epromotes natural collagen production, supports cartilage regeneration, and provides \u003cbr\u003eessential cushioning to keep joints smooth and flexible \u0026amp; improve absorption. The inclusion of Vitamin K2-7 further boosts effectiveness by guiding calcium toward the bones, helping improve joint strength and mobility. Together, Glucosamine, Chondroitin, and MSM work synergistically to support cartilage structure, ease everyday stiffness, and promote overall joint comfort. This powerful combination helps enhance flexibility, support movement, and maintain joint well-being for an active lifestyle\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Smart Pack - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":48003810525354,"sku":"NGLS60","price":599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/best_glucosamine_supplement.webp?v=1770876635"}],"url":"https:\/\/neuherbs.com\/collections\/speciality-supplements.oembed","provider":"Neuherbs","version":"1.0","type":"link"}